{"tid":557021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"因應大埔車禍 紅十字會籲捐血","createTime":"2018-02-11T03:36:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-12T01:59:57.000Z","uid":1221,"like":5,"dislike":146,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"4733925b22cc50db79e7e259e55625317818c528","tid":557021,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T03:36:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Mb4XED6wUuH8mNrpl0513g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjMwO2g9MzU1O2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/News/now.com/253721_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FMb4XED6wUuH8mNrpl0513g--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjMwO2g9MzU1O2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2FNews%2Fnow.com%2F253721_1.jpg&h=28664022&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】因應大埔公路車禍，紅十字會呼籲市民捐血。<br />\n<br />\n紅十字會輸血服務中心指，因應大埔公路車禍及全港公立醫院使用率上升，血液需求處於極高水平，血液供應面對巨大壓力。紅十字會呼籲16至66歲、體重超過41公斤而又健康的市民前往捐血。銅鑼灣、荃灣及觀塘捐血站將延長服務時間至晚上八時。<br />\n<br />\n2018年2月11日 上午10:00"},{"pid":"32dc3761603a763bdb52f675b818ded9df30c11f","tid":557021,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T03:37:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ff7aac1d97faa49bd2cb28b939e30a72cb7696","tid":557021,"uid":29314,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T03:38:06.000Z","msg":"收皮啦！紅十字會！"},{"pid":"dc5d6914dde0b4b984f77694478601531adddea8","tid":557021,"uid":8048,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T03:39:14.000Z","msg":"借題發揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ba73eee48f9a883b8c22bb577d01b09f4182c73","tid":557021,"uid":17859,"like":80,"dislike":5,"score":75,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T03:40:09.000Z","msg":"難得有人幫手清理低端人口<br